---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Welcome to Pet Toy Fun Zone" description="Discover a world of vibrant, whimsical toys designed to keep your pets entertained and joyful. Explore our collection of fun pet toys today!">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <div class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-[#FF9500] to-[#FF6B00] py-20 md:py-32">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full opacity-10">
      <div class="absolute top-10 left-10 w-32 h-32 rounded-full bg-white animate-pulse"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-20 right-20 w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-white animate-bounce"></div>
      <div class="absolute top-1/3 right-1/4 w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-white animate-ping"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          Welcome to <span class="block bg-[#00D4AA] text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg inline-block mt-4 transform -rotate-3">Pet Toy Fun Zone</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-white font-medium mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Fun Toys to Keep Your Pets Happy and Playful
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="#explore" class="bg-[#00D4AA] hover:bg-[#00B894] text-white font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-full text-xl transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg">
            Explore Toys
          </a>
          <a href="#features" class="bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 text-[#FF9500] font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-full text-xl transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg">
            Why Choose Us
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Introduction Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <div class="inline-block bg-[#00D4AA] text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-full mb-6">
          <i class="fas fa-paw text-2xl mr-2"></i>
          <span class="text-xl font-bold">Pet Paradise Awaits</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#FF9500] mb-6">
          Dive into a Colorful Adventure!
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Where your furry, feathery, or scaly friends can unleash their inner wild child! At Pet Toy Fun Zone, we believe every pet deserves a playground of whimsy and wonder. Our vibrant collection features everything from bouncy balls that zoom like shooting stars to plush pals that spark endless cuddles and chases.
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-[#00D4AA] rounded-full"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Features Section -->
  <section id="features" class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-[#FFF5E6]">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#FF9500] mb-4">Why Choose Our Toys?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Because playtime should be safe, fun, and full of wonder for every pet!
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Feature 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-3 transition-all duration-300 border-4 border-[#00D4AA]">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-[#FF9500] flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt text-3xl text-white"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center text-[#FF9500] mb-4">Durable & Safe</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-center">
            Crafted with pet-loving care, using non-toxic materials that withstand even the toughest play sessions.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Feature 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-3 transition-all duration-300 border-4 border-[#FF9500]">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-[#00D4AA] flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
            <i class="fas fa-paw text-3xl text-white"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center text-[#FF9500] mb-4">Variety for All Pets</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-center">
            Toys tailored for dogs, cats, birds, and more â€“ because playtime knows no species boundaries!
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Feature 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-3 transition-all duration-300 border-4 border-[#00D4AA]">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-[#FF9500] flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
            <i class="fas fa-paint-brush text-3xl text-white"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center text-[#FF9500] mb-4">Whimsical Designs</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-center">
            Bright colors and imaginative shapes to ignite curiosity and joy in your pets.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Toy Categories Preview -->
  <section id="explore" class="py-20 bg-[#FFF5E6]">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#FF9500] mb-4">Discover Our Toy Collection</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Toys for every pet personality and play style!
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <!-- Category 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FF9500] to-[#FF6B00] flex items-center justify-center">
            <i class="fas fa-bone text-6xl text-white"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#FF9500] mb-2">Chew Toys</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Perfect for teething puppies and persistent chewers</p>
            <a href="#" class="text-[#00D4AA] font-bold flex items-center">
              Shop Now
              <i class="fas fa-arrow-right ml-2"></i>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Category 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#00D4AA] to-[#00B894] flex items-center justify-center">
            <i class="fas fa-feather-alt text-6xl text-white"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#FF9500] mb-2">Plush Toys</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Soft cuddly companions for endless comfort</p>
            <a href="#" class="text-[#00D4AA] font-bold flex items-center">
              Shop Now
              <i class="fas fa-arrow-right ml-2"></i>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Category 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FF9500] to-[#00D4AA] flex items-center justify-center">
            <i class="fas fa-baseball-ball text-6xl text-white"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#FF9500] mb-2">Interactive Toys</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Engaging puzzles and games for mental stimulation</p>
            <a href="#" class="text-[#00D4AA] font-bold flex items-center">
              Shop Now
              <i class="fas fa-arrow-right ml-2"></i>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Category 4 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#00D4AA] to-[#FF9500] flex items-center justify-center">
            <i class="fas fa-cat text-6xl text-white"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#FF9500] mb-2">Cat Essentials</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Everything your feline friend craves for play</p>
            <a href="#" class="text-[#00D4AA] font-bold flex items-center">
              Shop Now
              <i class="fas fa-arrow-right ml-2"></i>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FF9500] to-[#00D4AA]">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
          Ready for Pet-tastic Fun?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-2xl text-white mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Join thousands of happy pets and their humans who've discovered the magic of Pet Toy Fun Zone!
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="bg-white text-[#FF9500] font-bold py-5 px-10 rounded-full text-xl inline-flex items-center transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 shadow-xl">
          <i class="fas fa-shopping-cart mr-3"></i>
          Shop Our Collection
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonials -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#FF9500] mb-4">Happy Pets, Happy Humans!</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Hear what our customers have to say about our toys
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
        <div class="bg-[#FFF5E6] rounded-2xl p-8 border-2 border-[#00D4AA]">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[#FF9500] flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold mr-4">
              M
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">Maggie & Max</h4>
              <div class="text-[#FF9500]">
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 italic">
            "Max destroyed every toy we bought until we found Pet Toy Fun Zone. These toys actually last! Maggie loves the squeaky hedgehog."
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
        <div class="bg-[#FFF5E6] rounded-2xl p-8 border-2 border-[#FF9500]">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[#00D4AA] flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold mr-4">
              S
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">Sophie & Luna</h4>
              <div class="text-[#FF9500]">
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 italic">
            "Luna was so bored until we got her the interactive puzzle toy. Now she's engaged for hours! Shipping was super fast too."
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
        <div class="bg-[#FFF5E6] rounded-2xl p-8 border-2 border-[#00D4AA]">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[#FF9500] flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold mr-4">
              J
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">Jake & Charlie</h4>
              <div class="text-[#FF9500]">
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-700 italic">
            "Charlie (our parrot) loves the colorful toys! Safe materials mean peace of mind, and the vibrant colors keep him engaged."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>